<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-8">
      <h1><%= @story.title %></h1>
      <p>Once upon a time <strong><%= @story.hero %></strong> was wandering in the vals of <strong><%= @story.location %></strong>.</p>
      <p>One day, our hero crossed the path of <strong><%= @story.enemy %></strong>, kicked that horrific person's ass and found a fabulous <strong><%= @story.treasure %></strong>.</p>
      <p>Our hero learned to code and lived long ever after.</p>
      <%= link_to "Back to stories", stories_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>